{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":53,"Text":"法老派遣征募者到各城市去。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":54,"Text":"他說：「這些人確是一小撮人。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":55,"Text":"他們確是激怒了我，"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":56,"Text":"我們確是謹慎的團體。」"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":57,"Text":"我就使他們離開許多園圃和源泉，"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":58,"Text":"財寶和高貴的住所。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":59,"Text":"（事情）是像那樣的。我使以色列的後裔繼承它。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":60,"Text":"敵人在日出時趕上他們。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":61,"Text":"當兩軍相望的時候，穆薩的同伙們說：「我們勢必要被敵人追上。」"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":62,"Text":"他說：「決不會的！我的主同我在一起，他將引導我。」"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":63,"Text":"我啟示穆薩說：「你應當用你的手杖擊海。」海就裂開，每一部分，像一座大山。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":64,"Text":"在那裡，我讓那些人逼近（他們）。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":65,"Text":"我拯救穆薩和他的全體伙伴。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":66,"Text":"然後，淹死了其餘的人。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":67,"Text":"此中確有一種蹟象，但他們大半不是信道者。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":68,"Text":"你的主確是萬能的，確是至慈的。"},{"SurahNumber":26,"VerseNumber":69,"Text":"你應當對他們宣讀易卜拉欣的故事。"}]}